# MetaMask Design System

This is the MetaMask Design System - an interactive component library built with Expo and React Native. Use these components and tokens when building MetaMask mobile UI.

## Design Tokens

Import tokens from `@/lib/tokens`:

```typescript
import { colors, spacing, borderRadius, typography } from "@/lib/tokens";
```

### Colors (Dark Theme)
- `colors.background.default` - #222325 (main background)
- `colors.background.alternative` - #121314 (sunken surfaces)
- `colors.background.section` - #31333A (cards, sections)
- `colors.text.default` - #FFFFFF (primary text)
- `colors.text.alternative` - #858B9A (secondary text)
- `colors.text.muted` - #686E7D (disabled text)
- `colors.primary.default` - #8b99ff (interactive elements)
- `colors.primary.muted` - #8b99ff26 (primary backgrounds)
- `colors.error.default` - #FF7584 (errors, destructive)
- `colors.success.default` - #4AE39E (success states)
- `colors.warning.default` - #FFD33D (warnings)
- `colors.border.default` - #9CA1AF (borders)
- `colors.border.muted` - #858b9a33 (subtle borders)

### Spacing (4px base)
- `spacing[1]` = 4px
- `spacing[2]` = 8px
- `spacing[3]` = 12px
- `spacing[4]` = 16px
- `spacing[6]` = 24px
- `spacing[8]` = 32px

### Border Radius
- `borderRadius.xs` = 4px
- `borderRadius.sm` = 8px
- `borderRadius.md` = 12px
- `borderRadius.lg` = 16px
- `borderRadius.pill` = 9999px

