## When Building New Screens

1. Start with the container using `colors.background.default`
2. Add appropriate components from the registry
3. Use `spacing` for all padding, margins, gaps
4. Use `borderRadius` for rounded corners
5. Keep text colors semantic: default, alternative, or muted
6. Test on the Canvas page to preview your composition

